{
  "stem": "10859.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had no way how to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you gonna ask me a question, why you were so many thousands of people in one place?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Couldn't you, at night, just break through the gate or break through the-- to-- to-- to-- to the tents, whatever they had, and just run away to the woods?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes, we could've done that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe 1,000 would've been killed and maybe 2,000 not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But what would happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Several thousand people, when they run away to the woods, what are you gonna do over there?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Where are you gonna-- what are you gonna eat?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It-- there was no way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Again, and then beside that, the people were so weak from the three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I knew I-- I-- I remember how I felt, which I was a young boy in the early 20s-- how weak, not eating, not drinking, not sleeping.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "How do you feel?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You give up life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't-- you don't have no more courage to fight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the truth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people don't understand this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's very hard to understand unless you lived through this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after on the third day, suddenly, it was like 10:00 in the morning-- 10:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We hear noises from-- big trucks came in-- everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And soon we look out through the window from the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we see that they take the women and the children and put them on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we also see that they-- 100 or 200 people at one time with a couple of Ukrainian police beside them, and they walk with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, at this moment, of course, I didn't know where were they going and where the machines were going with the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were, well, what-- what goes on here?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
